This paper deals with wireless communication systems and their performance analysis. Specifically, it focuses on the impact of uplink training on the performance of multi-cell multiple antenna systems with precoding. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), which deals with the fundamental limits of communication systems. The paper also involves networked systems, which suggests the category cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper discusses interference and optimization, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.MM (Multimedia), respectively. Finally, the paper involves communication protocols and algorithms, which could be categorized under cs.COM (Computers and Society).
